# Context Directory

Project-specific context generated by AIInitFramework.

## Expected Files

After running AIInitFramework, this directory will contain:

- ProjectOverview.md - High-level project description
- ObjectModel.md - Data model documentation  
- Automations.md - Triggers, Flows, Process Builders
- Integrations.md - External integrations
- SecurityModel.md - Profiles, Permission Sets, Sharing
- UIComponents.md - LWC, Aura, Visualforce
- BusinessProcesses.md - Business logic documentation

